{"tid":2139410,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【走入馬世界】嬲會咬人餓會扒地！仲會發咕嚕聲同其他馬打牙骱 #賽馬","createTime":"2020-08-04T09:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T09:06:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1b107e1a59e65709bae99a064d52f13d29d85a5f","tid":2139410,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/racing/20200803/UWVJP3FKOFHLXG76AJ2I4SSVK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2F20200803%2FUWVJP3FKOFHLXG76AJ2I4SSVK4%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=c306f29b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2F20200803%2FUWVJP3FKOFHLXG76AJ2I4SSVK4%2F&h=9957a0b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/racing/20200803/UWVJP3FKOFHLXG76AJ2I4SSVK4/</a><br />\n<br />\n【走入馬世界】嬲會咬人餓會扒地！仲會發咕嚕聲同其他馬打牙骱 #賽馬<br />\n<br />\n馬匹一舉一動都反映着其不同情緒變化<br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n馬匹屬於感情豐富的動物，一樣有喜、怒、哀、樂、緊張、舒服、信任、懷疑、頑皮各式各樣的情緒，但由於外型結構問題，只能表現在臉上、肢體與聲音。<br />\n<br />\n只需要學懂觀察馬匹眼睛、耳朵與動作，就能看出牠們所思所想，在賽馬世界裡無往而不利。<br />\n<br />\n馬匹天生安靜，但在受驚、受傷時會長鳴、唔舒服時則嘶吼、興奮時會噴氣、低鳴代表友善，同其他馬溝通時就會發出咕嚕聲。<br />\n<br />\n馬匹生氣或覺得討厭時，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n當害怕與興奮時會露出眼白，。。。。。。。。。，開心時當然會跑向你的方向。<br />\n<br />\n生病及沮喪耳朵同樣會背後向下，且。。。<br />\n。。。<br />\n<br />\n在馬格內，用屁股對着門口唔郁，90%是在打瞌睡，耳朵會微微向後，眼皮下垂。<br />\n<br />\n馬匹平時站着時，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n牠們只有在舒適情況下才會躺下睡覺，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lkUUdBKhxxGGAy_25UwMCaXWuv0=/190x171/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4TXJ36MUUTQMQND34SV6VL3IWU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlkUUdBKhxxGGAy_25UwMCaXWuv0%3D%2F190x171%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4TXJ36MUUTQMQND34SV6VL3IWU.jpg&h=60689684&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n退役馬期惑（右）一再在陣上企圖噬咬對手<br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n馬匹是感情豐富的動物<br />\n馬匹是感情豐富的動物<br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n馬匹碌地沙自尋歡樂<br />\n馬匹碌地沙自尋歡樂<br />\n(互聯網)</blockquote>"}]}